              "canCreateNewConnected": null,
              "connectedRepo": null,
              "connected_repo": null,
              "description": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"><strong>Este formulario está destinado a:</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"><strong>{{phase339322137.field415747619}}</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;\">Caso não esteja correto, por favor indique abaixo.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"caret-color: #000000; color: #000000;\">En caso de que no sea correcto, por favor indíquelo a continuación.</p>",
